metadata.name: Metropolis
metadata.description:
Parametric photography is a concept of mine conceived in 2020 from a research born in 2007, after 25 years of work and study on analog photography thanks to my work as a set designer, the project to create photographic sculptures was born.

These are the unique and unobtainable sketches in NFT. The collection will include 366 unique pieces, except for a few multiples of 5 ... an opportunity not to be missed as a true collector of certified works of art! ðŸ”¥ðŸ”¥ðŸ”¥
